07:54.120 --> 07:59.920
in the sense that as D-Roth theorists Georgios Kalas and Hugh March write, Inaris is what

07:59.920 --> 08:03.440
Urus is not, and Urus is what Inaris is not.

08:03.440 --> 08:08.840
Dispossessed possessed, barren lush, horizontal hierarchical.

08:08.840 --> 08:14.000
