12:25.160 --> 12:26.960
switched over to plant-based replacements.

12:26.960 --> 12:31.360
And how that ban might impact those indigenous to the Hawaiian islands?

12:31.560 --> 12:35.480
He himself had never liked the idea of the plant-based proteins of meat being made and

12:35.480 --> 12:39.200
